
Installation of LAMP Stack on VM Slave-1

SSH onto server 

ssh @vagrant10.10.45.11

Run yum update to update the yum repo

1— installed apache

Sudo yum install http

—Start the apache service

systemctl start httpd

—enable apache to start on reboot

sudo systemctl enable httpd.service

— install MySQL: MariaDB

sudo yum install mariadb-server mariadb

— start mariadb service

sudo systemctl start mariadba

—securing mariadb

sudo mysql_secure_installation

—Install PHP

sudo yum install php php-mysql

https://hostadvice.com/how-to/how-to-install-lamp-stack-on-centos-7/


 

